short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use Data360SE to search for information from Data360 Catalog

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you are a user of Data360 of Precisely you will love this.

With this extension you get seamless access to Data360 metadata from within your web-based reporting tools, applications and websites.

Now you can easily detect if there is information available about the business - and data assets you are working with.

Finding asset metadata is as simple as clicking on a word or phrase of interest. Easily click-thru to Data360 to gain an even deeper understanding and knowledge of your data assets.

This plugin is a courtesy of Intodq2.  We highly appreciate questions and enhancement requests. You can send these to support@intodq2.com.
